metadata.name: Matrix of Incomplete Voxels - Vue 01
metadata.description:
First ever art installation in the Metaverse.
This site-specific work of art is created on The Sandbox Metaverse and has an interrelationship with this Digital world.
In this world of entertainment this Installation is designed to be walked around and contemplated in order to to provide a poetic experience. 

This first art installation aims to continue to exist as it is in the metaverse for at least the next 50 years.
[Artist Website Link](http://denis-santelli.com/matrix-of-incomplete-voxels/)
